YPoWS_GL04XF0U4u5GGnfel6oLKnL1JgWQZE-qUXdwbfR4qgH-Iln5tP9To8F4hqmZl32L4TvHk=
xPsCGeFTPCBCfsHWduRCTJySZmZT2yT--_wBpLxzyQ] is making this possible). Peopl=
e will be hired and rewarded based on trackable contributions instead of tr=
aditional credentials.=C2=A0
At the simplest level, BaaG is just a shiny new interface on top of existin=
g tools that makes work feel more fun. One way to think of it is, =E2=80=9C=
What if developers built business-in-a-box software in the Unreal Engine [h=
