; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0;"><strong>Life Imitates Sci-Fi</strong></h3><p st=
yle=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em =
0;"><strong>Would it be possible to run a real business in a way that feels=
 like playing a video game?</strong></p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-si=
ze: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">This question has been swi=
mming around in my head for the past few weeks, probably because I&#8217;ve=
 been reading too much sci-fi.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16=
px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Before it was a terrible movie, =
<em><a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMtuhCAUhp9Glga5DS5YtGl=
Muumql6VBOJ0hChjAGvv0xZlFEwI5t__j_EYXuMZ0qDXmgrYMaXRWdYJIylmPrGK2k1wil8fvBO=
C1W1RJG6B1mxZndHEx3CcwJhzdFOWCGzJRxi6EfQvKLoKDwdIYi4UGiU7OqDfrIBhQ8APpiAHQo=
