-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">But thirty-four years later, in 2019, th=
e US Army began actively <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkM=
uOwyAMRb-m7IiAhJYsWMxmfiPi4aaoCURgEuXvh7SLkSzZ8kPn-jqDMKd86i0VJLVAnoLX_C5UL=
4eReD14rqQioUzPDLCasGjMFchW7RKcwZDi54IxIclLs1Eo_2B3qyRTkisrmX3cB8-e3POeM3Jx=
